<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="vi">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Thanh toán</title>
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com" />
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Poppins:wght@300;400;600&display=swap" rel="stylesheet" />
    <style>
        body {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            font-family: "Poppins", sans-serif;
            background: #f3f6ff;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            height: 100vh;
        }

        .container {
            background: #ffffff;
            max-width: 500px;
            width: 90%;
            padding: 40px;
            border-radius: 20px;
            text-align: center;
            box-shadow: 0 8px 25px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08);
            animation: fadeIn 0.8s ease;
        }

        @keyframes fadeIn {
            from {
                opacity: 0;
                transform: translateY(20px);
            }

            to {
                opacity: 1;
                transform: translateY(0);
            }
        }

        .icon {
            width: 100px;
            height: 100px;
            border-radius: 50%;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            margin: 0 auto 20px;
            font-size: 50px;
            color: white;
            animation: scaleIn 0.5s ease;
        }

        @keyframes scaleIn {
            0% {
                transform: scale(0);
            }

            100% {
                transform: scale(1);
            }
        }

        .success {
            background: #4caf50;
        }

        .failure {
            background: #f44336;
        }

        h2 {
            margin-top: 10px;
            font-size: 26px;
            font-weight: 600;
        }

        p {
            color: #555;
            margin: 10px 0 25px;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }

        .order-info {
            background: #f8faff;
            padding: 15px;
            border-radius: 12px;
            margin-bottom: 25px;
            border: 1px solid #e0e6ff;
        }

        .btn {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 12px 20px;
            color: white;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 12px;
            font-weight: 600;
            transition: 0.25s;
        }

        .btn-home {
            background: #4f46e5;
        }

        .btn-home:hover {
            background: #4338ca;
        }

        .btn-retry {
            background: #f44336;
        }

        .btn-retry:hover {
            background: #d32f2f;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>

    <!-- Thanh toán thành công -->
    <div class="container" id="success">
        <div class="icon success">✓</div>
        <h2>Thanh toán thành công!</h2>
        <p>Cảm ơn bạn đã đặt hàng. Đơn hàng của bạn đã được xử lý và đang được chuẩn bị giao.</p>

        <div class="order-info">
            <p><strong>Mã đơn hàng:</strong>
                <%= data.order_code %>
            </p>
            <p><strong>Tổng tiền:</strong>
                <%= data.grand_total.toLocaleString('vi', {style : 'currency' , currency : 'VND' }); %>
            </p>
        </div>

        <a href="http://127.0.0.1:5500/" class="btn btn-home">Quay lại trang chủ</a>
    </div>
</body>

</html>